  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章 导言：怀旧的时代",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23600584_3_2489-2656",
          "range": "2489-2656",
          "rangeStart": 2489,
          "rangeEnd": 2656,
          "markText": "她认为，眼下“全球都在流行这种怀旧病，越来越多的人渴望拥有一种集体记忆的共同体情感，渴望在一个碎片化的世界中获得一种连续性”；这种流行病是“身处生活与历史加速剧变的时代中的人们的一种防御机制”（p.xiv）。而这种“防御机制”的实质，在于“承诺重建今天诸多有影响的意识形态一味主张的理想家园，引诱我们放弃批判思考，而代之以情感团结”。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1722508682,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-01 18:38:02",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2489&rangeEnd=2656",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2489&rangeEnd=2656"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_4_20852-20921",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "20852-20921",
      "markText": "暴力的病态吸引力，在于可以暂时缓解暴力行为者自己因为处于次要地位、不利地位——弱势、不幸、无事可做、无足轻重、无存在感——而产生的屈辱感。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20852&rangeEnd=20921",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20852&rangeEnd=20921"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_5_11183-11266",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "11183-11266",
      "markText": "相反，记忆政治的做法，常常是使未来与过去互换性态，至少人们是这样对待它们的。在记忆政治中，过去变得柔韧，可随意操控，极易被塑造和重塑，并且这些都是记忆政治的基本特征。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11183&rangeEnd=11266",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11183&rangeEnd=11266"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_4_7944-8043",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7944-8043",
      "markText": "穆奇勒把这种背离传统作战方式的创新，追溯到权力的不断去疆界化，以及权力的不断的聚集。他说：“自由移动，如果有必要甚至可能移出他人能够到达的范围，以放弃对他人的责任，是我们这个时代的权力的核心特征。”",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7944&rangeEnd=8043",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7944&rangeEnd=8043"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_7_21238-21324",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "21238-21324",
      "markText": "现今的“情爱关系”，完全具有短暂、临时合约的所有特征，它绝对不是纯粹和明确的。但吊诡的是，“终身爱情关系仍是青年人与成年人的梦想。在现实中不能实现，往往只会使梦想更加生动”",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=21238&rangeEnd=21324",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=21238&rangeEnd=21324"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_4_14913-14985",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14913-14985",
      "markText": "个人与群体之间的关系，也就是追求归属的安全动机与追求自治的自我形构的魔力之间存在的一种爱-恨关系，在这种关系中人们时而寻求团结，时而又寻求分离。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14913&rangeEnd=14985",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14913&rangeEnd=14985"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_3_9770-9971",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9770-9971",
      "markText": "当人们在做怀旧之梦时，“回归”的通常并非过去本身，不是过去实际发生的事情，不是真实的过去，不是利奥波德·冯·兰克（Leopold von Ranke）建议史学家去恢复和再现的东西。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9770&rangeEnd=9971",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9770&rangeEnd=9971"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_7_8229-8312",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8229-8312",
      "markText": "视人们为必须主动为自己负责的个体，并把生活中遭受的挫败的责任完全转移到这些个体的肩膀上，最终导致了个人的风险和风险感急剧增加，导致了长期的焦虑进而导致了自恋主义倾向。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8229&rangeEnd=8312",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8229&rangeEnd=8312"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_3_6619-6713",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6619-6713",
      "markText": "随着旧的恐惧逐渐被遗忘，新的恐惧变得越来越大、越来越强烈。原来的上升现在却被视为堕落，原来的进步现在却被视为倒退，游戏中那些日益增多的并非出于本意的被利用的炮灰注定——或自我感觉——要失败",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6619&rangeEnd=6713",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6619&rangeEnd=6713"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_3_12283-12383",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "12283-12383",
      "markText": "每个人自己的方案的目标，不再是要建设一个更美好的社会，而是要改善自己在这个实际上显然无可救药的社会中的位置；不再是通过集体努力进行社会改革并从中获得回报，而是通过个人之间的争斗实现个人对战利品的占有。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12283&rangeEnd=12383",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12283&rangeEnd=12383"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_5_1736-1798",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1736-1798",
      "markText": "为什么人口群体之间的差异，总是会导致一种优越-低劣关系？其原因就是部落主义”; “这种部落的目的，就是决定支持谁和杀死谁”。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1736&rangeEnd=1798",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1736&rangeEnd=1798"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_6_10730-10803",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10730-10803",
      "markText": "昨天提升自己社会地位的成功，当在今天受到阻挠而不能继续上升时，就会吊诡地导致和强化被歧视感，进而使人萌生不满，增加了要迫切地矫正这种不平等的意愿。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10730&rangeEnd=10803",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10730&rangeEnd=10803"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_4_4918-4995",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4918-4995",
      "markText": "权力斗争的首要利害或根本目标，就是划分（以及根据需要而随意划分）合法的与非法的、许可的与禁止的、法定的与犯罪的、可容忍的与不可容忍的强制惩罚的界线的权利。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4918&rangeEnd=4995",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4918&rangeEnd=4995"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_4_6825-6875",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6825-6875",
      "markText": "在一个因信息高速公路而纵横勾连的世界中，独立于其他民族将面临可怕的命运，而独善其身也是根本不可能的。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6825&rangeEnd=6875",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6825&rangeEnd=6875"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_7_11826-11924",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "11826-11924",
      "markText": "这种新的道德，已经从向心性的道德变成离心性的道德，即道德曾经是弥合人际鸿沟、缩短人际距离、促进人际整合过程的首要黏合剂，但现在却成为造成现在严重的且还在不断恶化的分割、隔绝、疏离和撕裂的首要原因。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11826&rangeEnd=11924",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11826&rangeEnd=11924"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_5_10642-10690",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10642-10690",
      "markText": "政治一旦被剥夺了影响和建构未来的权力，往往就会被转换成集体记忆的空间，一种极易被篡改和操控的空间",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10642&rangeEnd=10690",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10642&rangeEnd=10690"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_3_6358-6398",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6358-6398",
      "markText": "但是，我们发现，这种私人化或个体化，却是以牺牲国家提供的社会服务和保护为代价的。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6358&rangeEnd=6398",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6358&rangeEnd=6398"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_6_6737-6831",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6737-6831",
      "markText": "温水煮青蛙式的剥夺所导致的痛苦和怨愤，会因为贫富分化的日益明显而转变成猛烈的愤怒，使星星之火渐呈燎原之势，进而使社会陷入习惯性的恶性循环，而只有进行革命性的变革，才能打破这种习惯性的循环。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6737&rangeEnd=6831",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6737&rangeEnd=6831"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_7_3963-4014",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3963-4014",
      "markText": "我们已经被拖进那些毫无意义的占有、迷恋和惯例之中，我们逐渐认为它们是确证我们虚幻地位和状态的万灵药方。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3963&rangeEnd=4014",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3963&rangeEnd=4014"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_8_8130-8168",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8130-8168",
      "markText": "只有当我们知道我们不是谁，以及只有我们知道我们反对谁时，我们才知道我们是谁。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8130&rangeEnd=8168",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8130&rangeEnd=8168"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23600584_3_1983-2034",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1983-2034",
      "markText": "当下，正是“未来”因不可信、不可控而遭受谴责、嘲笑而成为失信者的时候，也正是“过去”成为可信者的时候。",
      "totalCount": 55,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23600584&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1983&rangeEnd=2034",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e2b32fb071681dc8e2bbd45?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1983&rangeEnd=2034"
